verses.text: \w A|strong="H3068"\w* canticle \w for|strong="H7442"\w* David himself, \w when|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* house \w was|strong="H3068"\w* built after \w the|strong="H3068"\w* captivity. \w Sing|strong="H7442"\w* ye \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* new canticle: \w sing|strong="H7442"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*, all \w the|strong="H3068"\w* earth.

Sing ye \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Lord \w and|strong="H6440"\w* bless \w his|strong="H6440"\w* name: shew forth \w his|strong="H6440"\w* salvation \w from|strong="H6440"\w* day \w to|strong="H6440"\w* day.
Declare \w his|strong="H3605"\w* glory \w among|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Gentiles: \w his|strong="H3605"\w* wonders \w among|strong="H5921"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* people.

\w For|strong="H0776"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H0834"\w* great, \w and|strong="H0776"\w* exceedingly \w to|strong="H3027"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* praised: \w he|strong="H0834"\w* \w is|strong="H0834"\w* \w to|strong="H3027"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* feared above all gods.

\w For|strong="H3027"\w* all \w the|strong="H0834"\w* gods \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* Gentiles \w are|strong="H0834"\w* devils: \w but|strong="H0834"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* Lord \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* heavens.

\w Praise|strong="H1288"\w* \w and|strong="H0935"\w* beauty \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w before|strong="H6440"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*: holiness \w and|strong="H0935"\w* majesty \w in|strong="H0935"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* sanctuary.

Bring ye \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Lord, \w O|strong="H8085"\w* ye kindreds \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Gentiles, bring ye \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Lord glory \w and|strong="H0430"\w* honour:
Bring \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* Lord glory unto \w his|strong="H7185"\w* name. Bring up sacrifices, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* come into \w his|strong="H7185"\w* courts:

Adore ye \w the|strong="H0834"\w* Lord \w in|strong="H0001"\w* \w his|strong="H0834"\w* holy court. Let \w all|strong="H1571"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* earth \w be|strong="H1571"\w* moved \w at|strong="H7200"\w* \w his|strong="H0834"\w* presence.

\w Say|strong="H0559"\w* ye \w among|strong="H1755"\w* \w the|strong="H0559"\w* Gentiles, \w the|strong="H0559"\w* Lord hath reigned. \w For|strong="H3045"\w* \w he|strong="H3808"\w* hath corrected \w the|strong="H0559"\w* world, which \w shall|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* moved: \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* judge \w the|strong="H0559"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w with|strong="H3045"\w* justice.

Let \w the|strong="H0834"\w* heavens rejoice, \w and|strong="H0935"\w* let \w the|strong="H0834"\w* earth be glad, let \w the|strong="H0834"\w* sea be \w moved|strong="H0935"\w*, \w and|strong="H0935"\w* \w the|strong="H0834"\w* fulness thereof:
The fields and all things that are in them shall be joyful. Then shall all the trees of the woods rejoice
Before the face of the Lord, because he cometh: because he cometh to judge the earth. He shall judge the world with justice, and the people with his truth.
